div class="t m4b7 x92 he ya23 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">believed Christ&apos;s word, believed that he was made whole, and </div><div class="t m1177 x2 h1 y1410 ff1 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">71 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
